    "biography": "<p>A crocodile-like dracoform (Crocodylus cymri) with a flat beaver-like tail, roughly 3 m plus a 1.5 m tail and ~375 kg of green-brown muscle. It digs, lives semi-socially, and ambushes large prey — sheep, cattle, even people — from the water.</p><p><strong>Powers:</strong> Engulf, Enhanced Physical Attributes (Strength, 3×/day for [Essence]D6 turns), Enhanced Senses (Low-Light Vision, Smell), Hardened Armor, Search</p><p><em>Attacks: 10S (gripping bite). Habitat: Rivers and estuaries. Range: Wales and scattered parts of Europe. Gripping bite: opposed Strength tests to escape; the grip's Power rises +1 each Combat Turn. Swimming Quickness multiplier 4. Book stats: Body 10/4 (Hardened Armor 4), Intelligence 2/4. PAE p.11.</em></p>",
